CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 13, 2005

[Cite as 04/13/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1666.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2004-1740. State ex rel. White v. Petro.

In Mandamus and Procedendo. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnicic, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
